    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四下手",
        "武松",
        "蒋忠",
        "陆怀"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手同上，斜一字。蒋忠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒弟们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "松林去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒋忠挖门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，蒋忠，自夺了施恩的酒店，扬名天下。今日闲暇无事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒儿们，大家演拳上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手同演拳。蒋忠三笑。陆怀报上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，大事不好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事惊慌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们铺子里，来了一醉汉，把大奶奶夹在酒缸子里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他赶来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
